PrecisOrder (a) designating certain persons (Wildlife Officers, Park Rangers and Forest Officers) employed by the Department of Forestry, Lands and Wildlife of the Province of Alberta, as "FISHERY OFFICERS" for the purposes of the Fisheries Act, without any additional salary or emolument; and (b) revoking those made by Order in Council P.C. 1990-70 of January 18, 1990.
